    "timestamp": "2026-05-10T13:29:46.133000+00:00",
    "content": "**[How to Play]** https://discord.com/channels/1339575347032621191/1339575475676123188/1344072737051775057\n\n**[House Rules TL;DR]**\n\n50 character demon whisper, whisper groups, voting recovable until 30 minutes prior to EOD\n\n# **[Game Specific House Rules]**\n\n**[Demon Whisper]** Once per game, each Demon may send a 50 character anonymous \"Demon whisper\" to any player by DMing the ST the message and the recipient.\n\n**[Night Length]** If night runs for more than 1 hour and you are most responsible for this, I choose for you and I will be annoyed. This only applies if the previous day did not end early. You can whisper ST to privately pre-queue actions if you'd like (please do if you might not be around).\n\n**[Whispers]** Each player is limited to 5 whispers (private conversations, via Discord DM) per day. N-party whispers cost each party (N-1) whispers, e.g. a 3-way whisper costs each player two whispers. You do not need to log whispers with the Storyteller for any reason. Please include me in all whispers for potential Pixie madness.\n\n**[Neighbor Whispers]** You may whisper for free and unlogged with your two neighbors. Neighbor whispers can continue through the night as long as information from that night is not shared.\n\n# **[House Rules]**\n\n**[Against Exact Evidence]** Please refrain from providing exact evidence such as screenshots, exact quotes, or exact timestamps of whispers with players or the Storyteller. These are unusually convincing, hard to bluff, and could not be replicated in an IRL game.\n\n**[Night Chat]** You are allowed to chat in game-chat at night. However: You cannot talk about your night information until morning.\n\n**[Voting]** Votes this game are revocable until 30 minutes before end of day; react with ⬆️ to place a vote. Discretion is applied if many votes occur near lock time/EOD, etc.\n\n**[Day Length Adjustment]** Upon request, I may create a poll to extend a day by 24hrs. React to a nomination with ⏩ if you would like to fast forward on that nomination. Day adjustment requirements are at my discretion and will protect the interests of dead voters.\n\n# Jinxes\n\n**[Magician x Marionette]** If the Magician is alive, the Demon doesn't know which neighbor is the Marionette.\n\n**[Magician x Legion]** Legion knows if a Magician is in play, but not which player it is.\n\n# Custom Jinxes \n\n**[Vortox]** If you hard Vortox check day 1(not executing to see if it's a Vortox game) and Vortox is in play, I may continue the game for a few days before announcing evil has won.\n\n**[Goblin]** If a player claims goblin less than 30 minutes before or during vote lock, votes will be unlocked on their nomination only for 30 minutes and day might be extended. Goblin must be claimed within 5 minutes of seeing their nomination to count.\n\n**[Mez]** The Mez word must be said in public chat.\n\n**[Legion X Magician]** If both Magician and Legion are in play, Legion do not get demon whispers.",
